The paper deals with the classification of tabla strokes using decision tree, ID3 and random forest classifiers. This involves the extraction of features and the use of machine learning algorithms for classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
